{
  "message": "\ud83d\udc1b Fix Playwright build failure: pin TypeScript ~6 and remove deprecated baseUrl (#10689)\n\nTS 7.0 dropped support for baseUrl, breaking the Playwright E2E build step.\nPin typescript to ~6.0.3 (patch-only) to prevent accidental major upgrade,\nand remove baseUrl + ignoreDeprecations from tsconfig since paths works\nstandalone with moduleResolution: \"bundler\".\n\nFixes the \"TS5101: Option 'baseUrl' is deprecated\" build error in CI.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
  "files": [
    {
      "sha": "28b290fd556a1d40ff65e05d350156b73710d604",
      "filename": "web/package.json",
      "status": "modified",
      "additions": 1,
      "deletions": 1,
      "changes": 2,
